{"id":219299,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/global-voices-印度：世界上最后一份手抄报纸/","date":"2012-04-04T06:43:16Z","modified":"2012-04-04T06:43:16Z","title":"Global Voices | 印度：世界上最后一份手抄报纸","content":"<p><p>最早开始的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Newspaper\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Newspaper\">报纸</a>是用手抄的，而现在印度青奈的乌尔都语晚报“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Musalman\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Musalman\">The Musalman</a>”也许是现今世界上最后一份仍在用手抄的报纸。“The Musalman”晚报是由Chenab Syed Asmadullah Sahi于1927年建立，并在印度青奈内每日发行至今。</p>\n<p>目前晚报由Chenab Syed Asmadullah Sahi的孙子Syed Arifullah以及六位精通书法誊写的工作者经营，他们负责抄写这份每日发行四张，发行量约二万三千份使用乌尔都语的报纸，内容横跨包括政治、文化与运动。</p>\n<p>随着近来科技的蓬勃发展，人们在網絡上阅读新闻，报纸即将面临存活的困境，如此手感的接触已经很难找到了。这份报纸目前订价<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.theweekendleader.com/Culture/610/Handwritten-paper.html\" href=\"http://www.theweekendleader.com/Culture/610/Handwritten-paper.html\">0.7卢比</a>，相当于2分美金。</p>\n<div><img title=\"Signboard of the office. Screenshot from the video The Musalman\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/The-Musalman1-375x209.jpg\" alt=\"Signboard of the office. Screenshot from the video The Musalman\" width=\"375\" height=\"209\" /></p>\n<p>办公室的招牌。截图来自影片 The Musalman</p>\n</div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://tarunjimm.blogspot.com/2012/03/musalman-hand-written-urdu-daily.html\" href=\"http://tarunjimm.blogspot.com/2012/03/musalman-hand-written-urdu-daily.html\">MadanMohan Tarun</a>介绍道：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>目前编辑是Syed Arifullah先生，在他父亲死后掌管这份工作，他父亲经营这份报纸超过四十年时间，而由他的祖父于1927年创办。这份报纸没与乌尔都的数位化文字妥协而维持他最初的样貌。..</p>\n<p>誊抄每页报纸需要花费三小时，在收到兼任记者的英文新闻后，就被称为Katibs的书写者翻译为乌尔都语，致力于这项古老的乌尔都语的书法艺术，用笔在纸上述说故事。完成了背面附印后，写好的纸准备印刷了。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://luthfispace.blogspot.com/2011/05/musalman-and-its-fossilised-dream.html?showComment=1307011283384#c3258810310201499289\" href=\"http://luthfispace.blogspot.com/2011/05/musalman-and-its-fossilised-dream.html?showComment=1307011283384#c3258810310201499289\">Afsar Shaheen</a>回应了<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://luthfispace.blogspot.com/2011/05/musalman-and-its-fossilised-dream.html\" href=\"http://luthfispace.blogspot.com/2011/05/musalman-and-its-fossilised-dream.html\">Luthfispace的文章</a>说明为何微影印刷仍被使用：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>乌尔都语字体是非常困难的，并且电脑字型看起来比起手写还不雅，因此当其他语言改用电脑字体时乌尔都语仍使用微影印刷。</p>\n<p>电脑发明后，书写乌尔都语得到更大的鼓舞，他允许书法书写时不会有微影印刷的问题。至今，一本书或报纸由一位技艺精湛的katib誊写并使用微影来印刷是非常精巧与美观的，电脑并不适合书写乌尔都语。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>观赏这支由<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.ucfilms.in/subject/culture/the-musalman/\" href=\"http://www.ucfilms.in/subject/culture/the-musalman/\">Ishani K. Dutta</a>导演制作的影片，由印度外交部上传至<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LUmdx2YHGcA&#038;feature=share\" href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LUmdx2YHGcA&#038;feature=share\">Youtube</a>：</p>\n</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%84%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F04%2F10743%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F04%2F10743%2F&#038;desc=%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%BD%E6%89%8B%E6%8A%84%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F04%2F10743%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollo